				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "On approaching an ancient mural in the goblin camp, Shadowheart recognises it was once decorated to honour the moon goddess. Selûne. A worshipper of Selûne's rival, Shar, Shadowheart reacts with distaste and ill ease (if Shadowheart hasn't revealed her true nature yet, her observations are a little more veiled.)"
